Feature:  Testing API

Background:
    * def url_base = 'http://localhost:8070/playlists'

    Scenario: sucesso ao logar
    When: quando eu preencher campos
    And:a senha cadastrada
    Then: eu logo com sucesso e recebo 200 OK

(1)
Scenario: List All Playlists
When: given a read order Get method on url "/listAll"
Then: status 200 Ok

(2)
Scenario: Success find one playlist for id
When: given a read order Get method By a Valid PlaylistId on the url
Then: Status 200 Ok

(3)
Scenario: Fail find one playlist for id
When: given a read order Get method By a Invalid PlaylistId on de url
Then: Status 404 ObjectNotFound

(4)
Scenario: Success Create a new Playlist
When: Given a read order Post method with valid playlist name in the body
Then: Status 201 Created

(5)
Scenario: Fail Create a new Playlist
When: Given a read order Post method with invalid playlist name in the body
Then: Status 400 Bad Request

(6)
Scenario: Success Delete a Playlist
When: Given a read order Delete method with valid playlistId on url
Then: Status 200 Ok

(7)
Scenario: Fail Delete a Playlist
When: Given a read order Delete method with invalid playlistId on url
Then: Status 404 Not Found

(8)
Scenario: Success Rename a Playlist name
When: Given a read order Put method with valid playlist name in the body
And:  valid playlistId in the body
Then: Status 204 No Content

(9)
Scenario: Fail Rename a Playlist name
When: Given a read order Put method with invalid playlist name in the body
And: /Or invalid playlistId in the body
Then: Status 404 Bad Request

